only opinion. Posts which are not supported by additional testimony or incidents should be removed after the time limit for confirmation has elapsed. A forum reflects those who participate.  <p><a href="http://home.att.net/~smoke.boonvegas/sijandi/sijgreysig.jpg"target="web"><img src="http://home.att.net/~smoke.boonvegas/sijandi/sijgreysig.jpg" border="0"></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.showMessage?topicID=398.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.showMessage?topicID=389.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.emailToFriend?topicID=386.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend">Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.threadControl?topicID=386.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=386.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=386.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub4.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><b>jump to:</b><br><select name=forumName><option value="eqasylumgeneral">General<option value="eqasylumfrm25">Raid Discussions<option value="